nlp.upperlevel

Class MutualDisambiguation

  • java.lang.Object
    • nlp.upperlevel.MutualDisambiguation

  • public class MutualDisambiguation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class receives an WikimetaXMLDecoder Annotated Object, retrieves all the DBPedia or Wikipedia content for each link, and uses them to disambiguate. It is applied to a WikiMetaXMLDecoder object. (see SemLinker NIST KBP2013 paper for information!)
    Author:
    ericcharton
